opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 24th day of December, 2015, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED, and the Petition for Writ of Mandamus is DENIED.
Justice EAKIN did not participate in the decision of this matter.
